<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang='en-US'>
<head>
  <meta charset='utf-8' />
  <title>BitShift</title>
  <%= css :app %>
  <link href='/css/entypo.css' rel='stlyesheet' type='text/css' />
  <link href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lato' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' />
</head>
<body>
  <section class='introduction'>
    <header class='page-header'>
      <h1><%= img '/images/logo.png', :alt => 'BitShift' %></h1>
      <p class='spiel'>We build cool stuff.</p>
      <p class='sub-spiel'>We're a literal-not-figurative dynamic team of developers and designers that provides cutting-edge web solutions.</p>
      <p class='sub-spiel'>Yes, we accept <a href='http://bitcoin.org'>Bitcoin</a>.</p>
      <a class='check-us-out btn' href='#'>CHECK US OUT</a>
    </header>

    <ul class='aspect-list'>
      <li class='aspect'>Ruby</li>
      <li class='aspect'>JavaScript</li>
      <li class='aspect'>CSS</li>
      <li class='aspect'>Design</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class='about-us'>
    <div class='who-we-are'>
      <h2>Who We Are</h2>
      <p>We are truly a different type of web development consulting company. we have a team of brilliant developers and designers that use our dynamic, arbitrary individual tasking system to complete jobs in the most efficient way possible.</p>
    </div>

    <div class='how-we-roll'>
      <h2>How We Roll</h2>

      <ul>
        <li>
          <i class='entypo-chart-line'></i>
          We deliver results
        </li>

        <li>
          <i class='entypo-progress-2'></i>
          Task-driven
        </li>

        <li>
          <i class='entypo-heart'></i>
          We love what we do
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class='services'>
    <div>
      <h2><span>Services</span></h2>

      <div class='service'>
        <h3>Ruby</h3>

        <ul>
          <li>Ruby on Rails</li>
          <li>Sinatra</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class='service'>
        <h3>JavaScript</h3>

        <ul>
          <li>CoffeeScript</li>
          <li>node.js</li>
          <li>express</li>
          <li>jQuery</li>
          <li>Meteor</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class='service'>
        <h3>CSS</h3>

        <ul>
          <li>Sass</li>
          <li>Less</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class='service'>
        <h3>Design</h3>

        <ul>
          <li>Photoshop</li>
          <li>Illustrator</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class='service'>
        <h3>Git</h3>

        <ul>
          <li>(+ GitHub)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class='get-in-touch'>
    <%= img '/images/minimal-logo.png', :alt => '' %>
    <header>
      <h2>Have a project for us?</h2>
      <p>We'd love to hear from you.</p>
    </header>

    <form class='contact-form'>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <input type='text' placeholder='Name' />
        </li>

        <li>
          <input type='text' placeholder='Email' />
        </li>

        <li>
          <textarea placeholder='Message' rows='10'></textarea>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <button type='submit' class='btn'>Get in touch</button>
    </form>
  </section>
</body>
</html>

